text: Annandale () is a census-designated place (CDP) in Fairfax County, Virginia."Annandale CDP, Virginia" (Archive). U.S. Census Bureau. Retrieved on April 2, 2015. "2010 CENSUS - CENSUS BLOCK MAP: Annandale CDP, VA" The population of the CDP was 43,363 as of the 2020 United States Census. ==References== Category:Census-designated places in Virginia
